law.history: Repealed 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 393, sec. 11, effective January 1, 1995. -- 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 48, sec. 10, effective July 13, 1990. -- Amended 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 341, sec. 23, effective July 15, 1988. -- Amended 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 333, sec. 2, effective July 13, 1984. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 381, sec. 1, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 12, effective June 21, 1974.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Purge on county board's own knowledge -- Procedure.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/94). In Attorney General Opinion 94-42, it was concluded that 1994 Ky. Acts Ch. 393, which repealed this statute "will take effect on January 1, 1995, the date the National Voter Registration Act will take effect with respect to Kentucky."
